</i></b><br>\
</span><ul><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">This course will be a 95% &nbsp;in-person class adhering to the Georgia Tech class attendance policy.</span></div></li></ul><br><ul><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Attendance is important in this class, as the course is highly interactive and nearly every class involves group work and other participation.</span></div></li></ul><br><ul><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Each student is expected to actively engage in class on all scheduled days, as your participation is necessary for the success of your classmates.</span></div></li></ul><br><ul><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);"><span style="font-size: calc(var(--font-scale) * var(--font-size)); letter-spacing: 0em;">Non-attendance or not participating will cost you a grade in the attendance portion of the course.</span></span></div></li></ul><br><ul><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="font-size: calc(var(--font-scale) * var(--font-size)); letter-spacing: 0em; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">I will not be using an attendance sheet, but I will have a variety of individual's names that I will call on to answer questions at various times throughout the term.<span style="line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);"><u> If I call your name and you are absent, then you will lose 5 points</u>.</span></span></div></li></ul><br></column-unit><column-unit slot="2" span="4"><b><br>\
