<br>\
</i></b></span><ul><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">It is my job as an educator to make this classroom a safe one for its members.</span></div></li></ul><br><ul><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">I expect that everyone treats their peers with kindness and respect in this classroom.</span></div></li></ul><br><ul><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">We will discuss different perspectives. You may not always agree with a perspective, but try to be respectful of other values, beliefs, and identities.</span></div></li></ul><br><ul><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Repeated inappropriate or abusive comments and/or behavior will not be tolerated and will be reported to the Director of Graduate Studies and the Dean of Ivan Allen College.</span></div></li></ul><br><ul><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">If you feel I'm brushing off your views or if there's some other reason you are uncomfortable in the classroom, please reach out to me right away.</span></div></li></ul><br></column-unit><column-unit slot="3" span="2"></column-unit></column-set><br>\
