</span><span style="font-size: 30.0125px; color: rgb(68, 55, 21); letter-spacing: 0em;">2. In the case of an unexpected emergency, notify me as soon as possible afterward.<br>\
</span><span style="font-size: 30.0125px; color: rgb(68, 55, 21); letter-spacing: 0em;">3.Documentation is requested for extended or repeated absences.</span></div></column-unit></column-set><hr><column-set><column-unit slot="0" span="1"></column-unit><column-unit slot="1" span="3"><span style="color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Discussion Lead(15)</span></column-unit><column-unit slot="2" span="8"><ul><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">13-15:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div></li></ul><ol><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Shows full understanding of the reading materials and ability to critically identify and analyze main themes and concepts.</span></div></li><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Presentation is focused, clear, well-organized, and engaging.</span></div></li><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Utilizes a variety of types of media to support the discussion and engage the audience.</span></div></li><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Demonstrates original thought within the summary and critical analysis.</span></div></li><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Introduces new ideas or interpretations not covered within the text.</span></div></li></ol><ul><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="font-size: calc(var(--font-scale) * var(--font-size)); text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0em; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">9-12: &nbsp;</span></div></li></ul><ol><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="font-size: calc(var(--font-scale) * var(--font-size)); text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0em; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Demonstrates adequate understanding of the reading, providing a summary of major ideas and details.</span></div></li><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="font-size: calc(var(--font-scale) * var(--font-size)); text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0em; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Some major points may be lacking</span></div></li><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="font-size: calc(var(--font-scale) * var(--font-size)); text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0em; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Asks questions that partially deepen the discussion.</span></div></li><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="font-size: calc(var(--font-scale) * var(--font-size)); text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0em; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Responds and listens to group members but in ways that do not widely stimulate their responses.</span></div></li><li><div style="text-align: left"><span style="font-size: calc(var(--font-scale) * var(--font-size)); text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0em; color: rgb(68, 55, 21);">Minimal analysis and critical thinking.A great deal of the response is descriptive with little interpretive or original work in conjunction with the text.\
